ImpactTypeImpl
public interface ImpactType extends ModelElement
A representation of the model object 'Impact Type'. Impact type. E.g. add, modify, delete. Impacts may also be quantitative. E.g. an impact might be increase or decrease in capacity - load, storage, ...
